Set Up for Minecraft Account

From the CFF account that's already set up, open terminal / CMD as admin
Use the following commands to make the account:

net user Minecraft owl /add
net localgroup administrators Minecraft /add

After these commands have been made, switch to the Minecraft account (the password is owl)
Walk through the set up process, make sure to disable any information tracking that you can.

Download Minecraft here: 
https://aka.ms/minecraftClientGameCoreWindows

Install Minecraft. Log in using minecraft7@codeforfun.com  || Codeforfunfox1

Next, install Java:
https://download.oracle.com/java/25/latest/jdk-25_windows-x64_bin.exe

